Project Title:
FitHub CRM – Fitness Center Management System

Project Description:
The FitHub CRM system is designed to manage the operations of a fitness center using the Salesforce platform. The system helps administrators manage gym members, trainers, classes, and bookings efficiently.

Functional Requirements:

Manage member registration and membership details
Manage trainer information and availability
Schedule and manage fitness classes
Allow members to book classes
Track booking payments and payment status
Generate reports and dashboards for analytics

Non-Functional Requirements:

Cloud-based application built on Salesforce
Secure access control using Salesforce authentication
Easy-to-use Lightning user interface
Real-time data updates and reporting

Users of the System:

Gym Administrator
Trainers
Gym Members
